{"tid":2105583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽: 35+應該每區多比兩隊入閘防DQ!!","createTime":"2020-07-12T17:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T18:33:40.000Z","uid":252069,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd4cbff3f63bfe860044cfb653683d1b60c963b","tid":2105583,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"初選完咗<br />\n我諗今次咁多人投算係好有認受性<br />\n各準候選人應該都會信守之前嘅承諾排得後嘅就唔參選<br />\n但係我想講大家仲要面對DQ<br />\n如果35席真係得35隊, 是旦DQ一隊咪收工?<br />\n即係你打十三么, 我是旦槓你一隻番子你就早抖?!<br />\n冇理由唔做Plan B嘅<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我強烈建議每區協調按初選得票放多兩隊入閘<br />\n條件係要承諾如果到時無人被DQ佢哋就要棄選</span></span><br />\n咁先可以為DQ做多一手準備<br />\n有人話中共無論如何都唔會比35+發生<br />\nDQ又好直接送中都好到時咩方法都會不惜代價<br />\n被DQ呢個過程係向國際社會打同情牌嘅其中重要一環<br />\n但係學19才子話齋共產黨你讓佢三分佢一定攞到盡三分半<br />\n所以我哋絕對要寸步不讓<br />\n策略上可以做嘅全部做盡咁先正路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5960575ae4768d02cb429df861af8673d8ea28a","tid":2105583,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:37:15.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"71fd3a672ccd18ae49ef183eefd0882906bb5c23","tid":2105583,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"留名再研究"},{"pid":"71aa959ee56e964c297b99ac836fa56f1c6d5c3d","tid":2105583,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71fd3a672ccd18ae49ef183eefd0882906bb5c23","tid":2105583,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"留名再研究"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:38:56.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b3538defe76bf3ead99bd1bdf6a9063c1cdd12","tid":2105583,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12